	(text "PLEASE READ:\n\nThe display on the left is labelled with the pins that connect to the Pi Zero 2W (shown with labels).\n\nThe battery (shown with labels), connects to the converter board.\n\nThe board outputs to the Raspi Zero 2W (shown with wires).\n\nThe Pico 2 is then connected to the Pi Zero 2W for power and data (shown using wires).\n\nThe Pico 2 is connected to the custom matrix PCB using labels (shown with labels)."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
